This is a good place to put your data files.  

You can download a shareware copy of Doom from here:
https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/idstuff/doom/doom19s

Or you can download a shareware copy of Heretic from here:
https://www.doomworld.com/idgames/idstuff/heretic/htic_v12

You could also put your commercial WADs here, just make sure you don't distribute them!
